{"tid":1380619,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[軟攻] 任職私營公司既你，其實都可以寫匿名信","createTime":"2019-07-29T05:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T10:22:17.000Z","uid":218731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"714c6fe9a2bc569363dfd89a192ffbc8903a7c4f","tid":1380619,"uid":218731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:16:57.000Z","msg":"不過對象就係公司內全部同事，唔一定要致全港市民既，基本上單一寫字樓既職員人數過50人既公司都要send<br />\n<br />\n免費電郵大把得申請啦，真係驚比人起底既就買張太空卡先send<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n內容基本結構就係先以公司喺社會上既價值呀貢獻呀之類。<br />\n<br />\n然後就講下最近社會既議題，加埋五大訴求，再用三兩句將既公司價值連繫到社會議題，如果公司有公開既企業社會責任(CSR)，就參透下點樣透過CSR實踐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考下已有既公開信既用字，再加多幾個四字詞。<br />\n<br />\n可以既話最後提及下805可能會出現全港大罷工，宣傳下叫大家做好心理準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceed79347678ddc01f223d096b4294ee580d7e7c","tid":1380619,"uid":255222,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:17:53.000Z","msg":"CSR ? LGBT or green topics 就得 政治野佢地就不了"},{"pid":"14c8f46f4f5110b987a38d4c8871d0313e2e9403","tid":1380619,"uid":218731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ceed79347678ddc01f223d096b4294ee580d7e7c","tid":1380619,"uid":255222,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:17:53.000Z","msg":"CSR ? LGBT or green topics 就得 政治野佢地就不了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:26:17.000Z","msg":"CSR 唔得就諗下從價值觀入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d4028dc5f30574d1b7fbbe45575578091a2b29","tid":1380619,"uid":290385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:26:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73faa442ab55955e236bfbbb72f10229080da0f5","tid":1380619,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:27:34.000Z","msg":"大firm 人多就話姐<img src=\"/assets/f